name: shelly barger
text: The staff here is friendly and on top of it. They consistently go above and beyond to make sure we have a great experience every time we go in. The pizza is hot fresh and fast. The store is clean and the remodle looks great.They have done a great job turning the store around.

name: daniel g
text: The best pizza hut I've tried so far. Thank you and keep the good work. Oh and for those that are writing bad reviews because of what someone else said, you need to try it for your self and then come back and review.

text:

After reading an the negative reviews I don't even want to go there now! One good review ha not worth my time AN money. We won't be going there.  Good luck Pizza Hut sounds like your gonna need it.
